let latestSession = car_telemetry | where CarId == 1 |summarize arg_max(StartTime, *) by CarId | project SessionId;
car_telemetry
| where TelemetryPoint in ('Speed', 'Brake')
| where SessionId in (latestSession)
| make-series value = avg(toreal(Data)) on StartTime step 1s by LapId, TelemetryPoint
| order by LapId asc

let latestSession = car_telemetry | where CarId ==1 |summarize arg_max(StartTime, *) by CarId | project SessionId;
car_telemetry
| where TelemetryPoint in ('Speed')
| where SessionId in (latestSession)
| make-series value = avg(toreal(Data)) on StartTime step 1s by CarId, LapId
| order by CarId asc, LapId asc
| render timechart
